examples.en: The teacher smacked the student who had misbehaved.
He misbehaved in class and was sent to the principal's office.
In the past, some teachers would cane students who misbehaved.
Children knew that if they misbehaved they would get the cane.
In those days, schoolchildren got the birch when they misbehaved.
In the past, some teachers would resort to the cane when students misbehaved.
Grandpa told us that when he was a kid, if he misbehaved at all, his father would tan his backside with a belt.
